These thick yet lightweight paddle back gold hoops are 30mm in diameter with a sturdy secure clasp, easy to put on and take off making them the perfect earrings for everyday wear.
These timeless chunky hoops for women are crafted with 925 Sterling Silver Posts and plated in 14K Yellow Gold plating for a long lasting finish that is nickel free, lead free, and hypoallergenic.
